SUSPECTED gunmen have kidnapped Appolonia Amaechi, mother of Ikechukwu Amaechi, publisher of TheNiche Newspapers. The kidnappers are demanding N20 million as ransom before they can release her. The 79-year old retired teacher was abducted on Tuesday, March 3, in her country home at Ahiazu Mbaise local government area of Imo State around 8 pm. She is diabetic and had been in the kidnappersâ€™ den in the bush since Tuesday without her drugs. Source: Real News